---
source: crates/loom/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: "loom_help(&[\"note\", \"add\"])"
---
Append a single note to the spec

Usage: loom note add [OPTIONS] --text <TEXT> <LABEL>

Arguments:
  <LABEL>  Spec label

Options:
      --text <TEXT>       Note text
  -w, --workspace <PATH>  Workspace root. Defaults to the current working directory
      --host-key          Explicitly allow ambient host Git credentials and signing config
      --kind <KIND>       Note kind [default: implementation]
  -A, --agent <BACKEND>   Override the agent backend for this invocation [possible values: claude, pi, direct]
  -h, --help              Print help
